1356
01:51:18,903 --> 01:51:22,574
l was here with the only brothers l have left,

1357
01:51:22,657 --> 01:51:26,828
and that there's no way l was gonna desert them.

1358
01:51:26,911 --> 01:51:29,581
l think she'll understand that.

1359
01:51:29,664 --> 01:51:31,833
