01:54:54,244 --> 01:54:56,371
Not the worst idea, Captain.

1407
01:54:56,454 --> 01:55:00,250
But it all depends on knocking out the tank here, right?

1408
01:55:00,333 --> 01:55:03,253
So how do you plan on doing that?

1409
01:55:03,336 --> 01:55:04,838
Reiben's right.

1410
01:55:04,921 --> 01:55:07,924
As our esteemed colleague from the Airborne pointed out,

1411
01:55:08,007 --> 01:55:13,096
what we got here is spit wads, so how do we stop the tank?

1412
01:55:13,179 --> 01:55:14,889
Give it a rabbit to chase.

1413
01:55:14,973 --> 01:55:18,560
We could hit the tank in the tracks.

1414
01:55:18,643 --> 01:55:20,520
Yeah, but with what?

1415
01:55:22,897 --> 01:55:25,191
We could try a sticky bomb.

1416
01:55:25,275 --> 01:55:26,818
Sticky bomb, sir?

1417
01:55:27,944 --> 01:55:32,949
- Sir, are you making that up? - No. lt's in the field manual.

1418
01:55:33,032 --> 01:55:35,785
