rig up a simple fuse,

1426
01:55:56,931 --> 01:55:59,851
then coat the whole thing with axle grease.

1427
01:55:59,934 --> 01:56:02,520
When you throw it, it should stick.

1428
01:56:02,604 --> 01:56:05,398
lt's a bomb that sticks. A sticky bomb.

1429
01:56:05,482 --> 01:56:10,570
