1551
02:05:55,572 --> 02:05:59,742
lt goes out of his grasp and hits a kerosene lantern.

1552
02:05:59,826 --> 02:06:03,705
The thing explodes, and the whole barn almost goes up.

1553
02:06:19,262 --> 02:06:22,807
That was it...Dan went to Basic next day.

1554
02:06:22,891 --> 02:06:26,853
